Clone of Story activity from the Sugar enviroment.

Use images from Art4Apps project

The app will be configured on Android to be used with the sceen on 
vertical position, to allow display the on screen keyboard, 
the images and the text editor.

Used libraries:
* https://github.com/devongovett/pdfkit
* https://github.com/devongovett/blob-stream
* https://github.com/feross/buffer

